Kebakaran!

484
00:36:19.000 --> 00:36:20.360
Cepat padamkan apinya!

485
00:36:20.719 --> 00:36:21.880
Cepat!

486
00:36:22.159 --> 00:36:23.480
Ambil lebih banyak air lagi!

487
00:36:24.119 --> 00:36:24.760
Aku pergi menimba air!

