506
00:37:09.320 --> 00:37:12.719
Tolong aku!

507
00:37:12.719 --> 00:37:13.639
Ada orang di dalam.

508
00:37:13.800 --> 00:37:14.440
Cepat.

509
00:37:14.559 --> 00:37:15.360
Ada orang?

510
00:37:16.360 --> 00:37:18.360
